OL,5, Lego, the Danish toymaking giant, has  
OL,6, said it will stop operating in Russia  
OL,7, indefinitely due to "continued         
OL,8, extensive disruption".                 
OL,10,FThe firm stopped delivering products to
OL,11,FRussia in March following the invasion 
OL,12,Fof Ukraine, but its shops remained open
OL,13,Fas most rival retailers pulled out.    
OL,15,FLego said it would now end its         
OL,16,Fpartnership with Inventive Retail Group
OL,17,Fwhich runs 81 shops on Lego's behalf.  
OL,19,FIt did not mention Russia's invasion of
OL,20,FUkraine for pulling out of Russia.     
